                        <!-- MODIFIED: Updated content with detailed responsibilities list, including AI support and bolding the functions -->
                        <p>The Legal Operations team is dedicated to increasing the efficiency, transparency, and strategic impact of the Legal, Regulatory, & Compliance department.</p>
                        
                        <p>
                            Our primary functions include: 
                            <strong>Financial and Vendor Management</strong> (including Fiscal Year Planning and Budgeting), 
                            <strong>LRC Technology (including AI Support)</strong>, 
                            <strong>Data & Analytics</strong>, 
                            <strong>Knowledge Management</strong>, 
                            <strong>Org Design & Onboarding</strong>, 
                            <strong>Project Management, Task Automation, & Process Improvement</strong> (inc. M&A Integration), 
                            <strong>Shared Services</strong>, 
                            <strong>Strategic Planning</strong>, 
                            <strong>3rd Party Legal Services Program</strong>, 
                            <strong>Event Planning</strong>, and <strong>more</strong>.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>
                            Contact us early and often via our Service Desk when you need support with your business needs. Please submit all requests through the 
                            <a href="https://procoretech.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/114" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-800 font-semibold transition"><i class="fa fa-wrench mr-1"></i>LRC Service Desk</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- This link uses native HTML hash jump -->
                    <a href="#home" class="back-to-top">Back to Top &uarr;</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- SECTION 2: MEET THE TEAM (Polished Cards with Fixed Height) -->
            <section id="meet-the-team">
                <h2 class="collapsible searchable-item" data-target="team-content">
                    Meet the Team
                    <i class="ph-minus-circle-fill text-2xl transition-transform" data-icon></i>
                </h2>
                <div id="team-content" class="content-section">
                    <!-- Cards Grid: Ensures tiles are the same size. -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

